WEBVTT

00:00:06.954 --> 00:00:09.124
Izaberite kartu. Bilo koju.

00:00:09.124 --> 00:00:12.014
U stvari, uzmite ih sve
i pogledajte.

00:00:12.014 --> 00:00:15.848
Ovaj standardni špil od 52 karte
koristi se vekovima.

00:00:15.848 --> 00:00:18.098
Svakodnevno, hiljade ovakvih

00:00:18.098 --> 00:00:21.134
se meša u kazinima širom sveta

00:00:21.134 --> 00:00:23.719
i redosled karata se menja svaki put.

00:00:23.719 --> 00:00:26.431
Svaki put kad uzmete
dobro promešan špil

00:00:26.431 --> 00:00:27.642
kao što je ovaj,

00:00:27.642 --> 00:00:29.431
skoro sigurno ćete imati

00:00:29.431 --> 00:00:30.848
raspored karata